## npm install 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   npm install --save-dev @types/node                              types for node.js and typescript
  
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    npm install --save-dev nodemon                                    npm install -g nodemon
        "scripts": {
        "start": "nodemon index.ts"
        }
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    npm install express
    npm install --save-dev @types/express
